  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft from <span class=\"name name-special\">Mordite</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Fungal Mold</span>. Learn the blueprint with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Science Specialist</span> in a base.<br>Fungal Mold can be farmed, or found wild on <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">toxic planets</span>.<br>Mordite is harvested from the <span class=\"name name-fuel\">corpses of creatures</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-special\">腐藤</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">真菌霉</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>真菌霉可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒星球</span>上找到。<br>腐藤能从<span class=\"name name-fuel\">生物尸体</span>中被采集到。",
    "TencentChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-special\">腐藤</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">真菌霉</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>真菌霉可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒星球</span>上找到。<br>腐藤能从<span class=\"name name-fuel\">生物遗骸</span>中被采集到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-special\">歿鹽</span>及<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">蕈模</span>製作。在基地裡借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">科學專家</span>來了解設計圖。<br>蕈模可以在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">毒性星球</span>上栽種或於野外採集。<br>歿鹽則可於<span class=\"name name-fuel\">生物屍體</span>上採收。"
  },
